Request body to obtain a chart from a live algorithm. The /live/chart/read API accepts requests in the following format:

ReadLiveChartRequest Model - Request to body to obtain a chart from a live algorithm.
projectId integer
required
Id of the project that's live trading.
name string
required
Name of the chart to read.
count integer
required
The number of data points to request.
start integer
required
The unix start time of the request.
end integer
required
The unix end time of the request.
Example 
{
  "projectId": 0,
  "name": "string",
  "count": 0,
  "start": 0,
  "end": 0
}
